00:17:23,390 --> 00:17:26,659
Kelab Gyeongseong menghargai informasi berharga.

249
00:17:27,259 --> 00:17:28,989
Aku dalam proses mempelajarinya.

250
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,800
Kamu memiliki

251
00:17:35,370 --> 00:17:37,330
informasi tentang Young Jin?

