00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,719
apakah seseorang berpura-pura

273
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:05,590
menderita.

274
00:19:05,919 --> 00:19:07,890
Kamu punya informasi tentang Young Jin?

275
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:20,469
Parade akan melewati Gerbang Sakuradamon

276
00:19:21,509 --> 00:19:23,570
antara pukul 11.00 dan 12.00.

277
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:25,380
Di tahun 1860,

278
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:27,409
Perdana Menteri Jepang

279
00:19:27,479 --> 00:19:30,310
dibunuh di luar Gerbang Sakuradamon.

280
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,550
Hubungi Jepang.

281
00:19:34,179 --> 00:19:36,189
Gerbang Sakuradamon, pukul 11.00.

282
00:19:36,419 --> 00:19:37,449
Baik.

283
00:19:38,090 --> 00:19:39,459
Aku perlu berbicara denganmu.

284
00:19:39,959 --> 00:19:41,630
Polisi militer sudah tahu

285
00:19:41,689 --> 00:19:43,590
kamu sudah datang.

286
00:19:46,959 --> 00:19:49,130
Kapan koresponden itu tiba?

287
00:19:49,269 --> 00:19:50,570
Besok, pukul 10.00.

